<li>Litt et al., <i>Is the Brain a Quantum Computer?</i>, Cognitive Science (2006) <a href="http://watarts.uwaterloo.ca/~celiasmi/Papers/litt%20et%20al.2006.quantum%20brain.cogsci.pdf" class="external autonumber" title="http://watarts.uwaterloo.ca/~celiasmi/Papers/litt%20et%20al.2006.quantum%20brain.cogsci.pdf" rel="nofollow">[32]</a></li>
